      • getHandle

        public String getHandle()
        Get the handle of this texture.

        The texture must be loaded for this. (load(TextureRegistry) needs to have been called before)

        Returns:
        the texture handle of this
        Throws:
        IllegalStateException - if the texture was not loaded before.

      • getHandle

        public String getHandle​(Direction direction)
        Get the handle of this texture for the given direction.

        The texture must be loaded for this. (load(TextureRegistry) needs to have been called before)

        If no texture is available for this direction, the default texture is returned.

        Parameters:
        direction - the to get the handle for.
        Returns:
        the correct texture handle
        Throws:
        IllegalStateException - if the texture was not loaded before.
